        "description": "<p>Adds tags, categories, and excerpts to pages. Also adds pages to most views<br />\nthat list posts, such as the main view, tag archives, and the rss feed.</p>\n<p>The plugin has no settings, does not alter the database and only uses hooks<br />\nto achieve its goal. It also should work perfectly fine with Multisite<br />\ninstallations.</p>\n",
